quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  36,13,Give them an example of the People of the Town when the messengers came to it
  36,14,"When We sent them two [messengers], but they rejected them, so We strengthened them with a third, and they said, “We are sent to you as messengers.”"
  36,15,"They said, “You are no more than human beings like us, and the Most Compassionate has not sent down anything. You are simply lying.”"
  36,16,"They said, “Our Lord knows that we are sent to you as messengers"
  36,17,Our duty is only to convey the message clearly.”
  36,18,"The people said, “We consider you as an evil omen. If you do not desist, we will surely stone you, and we will inflict upon you a painful punishment.”"
  36,19,"The messengers said, “Your evil omen is with yourselves [because of your disbelief]. Is it because you are admonished? Rather, you are a people who transgress all bounds.”"
  36,20,"A man came from the farthest end of the city, rushing, and said, “O my people, follow the messengers"
  36,21,"Follow those who ask no recompense of you, and who are guided"
  36,22,Why should I not worship the One Who created me and to Whom you will all be brought back
  36,23,"Should I take besides Him other gods whose intercession cannot avail me in the least, nor can they come to my rescue, if the Most Compassionate wills to harm me"
  36,24,Surely I would then be clearly misguided
  36,25,"I believe in your Lord, so listen to me.”"
  36,26,"[But they killed him], so he was told, “Enter Paradise.” He said, “If only my people knew"
  36,27,"of how my Lord has forgiven me, and made me among the honored ones.”"
  36,28,"After his death, We did not send down any soldiers from the heaven against his people, nor did We have to do so"
  36,29,"It was no more than a single blast, and immediately they were extinguished"
  36,30,Alas for the humans! No messenger ever comes to them but they ridicule him
  36,31,Do they not see how many generations We destroyed before them who will never come back to them
  36,32,Yet all of them will be brought before Us